S.FORM: I 1956 a miheca saka 6 folad saka 28 a romi'ad masofoc ci Bakir Izetbegović , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Bosnia and herzegovina anini i ci Bakir Izetbegović, patirengan a romi'ad i 2016 a miheca saka 3 folad saka 17 a romi'ad.
